{
  "texts": [
    "While both sensory domains face common issues such as limited labeled data and high-dimensional inputs, their technical emphases and application contexts diverge in important ways.",
    "This table highlights these differences to better contextualize the role of AI and guide interdisciplinary development in sensory modeling.",
    "In addition to these parallel applications, growing interest has emerged around the integration of olfactory and gustatory cues within multisensory AI modeling.",
    "This area focuses on how olfactory inputs influence gustatory experiences.",
    "Neuroscientific studies have shown that flavor perception involves complex integration across brain regions such as the orbitofrontal cortex, which receives convergent input from both olfactory and gustatory pathways (Small and Prescott 2005)."
  ]
}